Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.42,0:00:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你講的是法律\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're parsing the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.32,0:00:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我講的則是精神層面的法則\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'm talking about a spiritual code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保密協議是一份契約\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Confidentiality is a covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.55,0:00:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不僅在我和接受我諮詢的人之間成立\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not only between myself and those I counsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.87,0:00:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我自己和上帝之間也成立\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but also between myself and the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉金博士  我現在重點關注的是洗錢案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dr. Larkin, my chief focus here is the money laundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.52,0:00:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果總統先生提到過馮山德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the President brought up Xander Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德·塔斯克  還有阿道希賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk, the Adohi Casino--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管重點是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It doesn't matter what the focus is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不能向你透露私人談話的內容\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't share anything we discussed privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宗教指導受法律保護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Religious guidance is protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.03,0:00:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你也提供專業的心理諮詢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you were also conducting professional therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我從未承認過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I never claimed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基斯先生及太太已經證實了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. And Mrs. Keith confirmed as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.37,0:00:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是去了他們家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We were at their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.56,0:00:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他們並沒有參與談話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But they didn't participate in any of our conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們又怎麼可能知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So how would they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你只提供宗教諮詢嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you're saying you only gave religious counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我對我工作的理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's how I choose to interpret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統夫婦從沒去過你的教堂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The President and his wife have never once attended your church.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至都和你不是一個教派的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're not even the same denomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.83,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無關緊要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法律上可緊要得很\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not legally speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對能說服法官發傳票給你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm certain I can convince a judge to issue a subpoena
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:01:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你並非總統夫婦正式的宗教導師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}on the grounds that you weren't their legitimate spiritual advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你的特權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is your prerogative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.53,0:01:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我會上訴  我肯定會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I can appeal. And I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你一定敗訴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You'd lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非對方放棄保密權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The only circumstance by which I would talk
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.82,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不會回答你的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is if someone personally waived their privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則我寧可被判蔑視法庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Otherwise I'd rather face contempt of court.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事關道德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a matter of ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統先生  你又把沙袋挪回來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. President. Ah, you brought it back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗洛伊德·梅威瑟{\fs14}[著名拳擊手]{\fs20}今早來白宮參觀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Floyd Mayweather visited the White House this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.17,0:01:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他看見這個肯定很興奮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought he'd get a kick out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他沒打幾拳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did he have a go at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他打了套組合拳  我都擔心把沙袋打爆了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He threw a combination I thought would bust the stitching loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那場面一定很好看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, that must have been a treat to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告訴我  這不僅僅是力量的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He was telling me it's not just about the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比他更有力量的拳手不少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Plenty of boxers are more powerful than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.50,0:01:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵是他的戰術  他的準頭和速度\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, it's his tactics, his precision, his speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的一點  就是他的反擊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Most important? His counter punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他躲閃騰挪  選擇最完美的時機一拳制勝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He dances and dodges and then picks the perfect moment to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著耳熟嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Does that sound familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you mean, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你送我這個沙袋  作為友誼的表示\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You gave this to me as a gesture of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在看著它  卻感受不到友誼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I look at this now, I don't see friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到的是算計\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I see calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你算計我  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You set me up, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的私下接觸  還有特別檢察官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your back channeling. The special prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再想想雷蒙德  琳達  還有吉姆·馬修斯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When I think about Raymond, about Linda, about Jim Matthews...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想錯了  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are wrong, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是鄧巴就婚姻諮詢問的問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Questions from Dunbar about the marriage counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"那是大海里的一根針  還不是鄧巴要找的那根"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"It's a needle in the haystack she's not trying to find."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的原話  她還真就撈著了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's what you said. Well, she found the needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常震驚  我絕沒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am shocked, sir. I -- I never --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你震驚才怪  你想削弱我的權威\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like hell you are. You want to deminish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.36,0:02:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,削弱你的權威\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Diminish you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為你2016年挑戰我打基礎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Laying the groundwork for a challenge in 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我無禮  但你這論調太荒唐了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am sorry to have to say this, sir, but you are being ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真以為我瞎了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you really think I'm so blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從沒有哪個副總統挑戰過在位總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A vice president has never challenged a sitting president.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你往上爬的過程中已經做過不少別人不會做的事了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've climbed the ladder doing things other men would never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是為了服務於你和本黨的利益\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Always in service to you and the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.35,0:03:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交出行程記錄是你的主意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was you idea to hand over those logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓白宮和中國扯上了關係  還有賭場\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You connected the White House to China, the casino --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.81,0:03:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雷蒙德·塔斯克讓我們與中國和賭場扯上了關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk entangled us with China and the casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.87,0:03:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是我及時干預\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if I hadn't intervened --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有弗洛伊德那套騰挪的本事  我識破你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't dodge and duck like Floyd. I've learned your moves now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當了總統就易多疑  你別這樣  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This office breeds paranoia. Don't give into it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不是會引人非議  我就會要求你辭職了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd ask for your resignation if it wouldn't make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但從此刻開始  我不想聽你的任何建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But from this moment forward, I don't want to hear your voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不想看見你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.26,0:03:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再讓我看見你  我就讓你吃不了兜著走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if I do, I will put you on your god damn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被驅逐了  我成功將總統和其他人隔開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Exile. I've managed to isolate the president from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括我自己\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Including myself.
