Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"夏普女眾議員淋漓盡致地展現了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Congresswoman Sharp is a  perfect example
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍方是如何將我們洗腦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of how the military brainwashes us
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從而絕對服從黨派路線的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}into never questioning the party line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她對法案的反對是可恥的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her opposition to the bill is disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會使數以千計的男性和女性\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It will cost thousands of men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得不到他們應得的公正\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14} the justice they deserve,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至會毀掉一些人的生活"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and some of them their lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都是梅根·漢納希的話  他們有失公正\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those are Megan Hennessey's words. They're biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是克萊爾教她說的  漢納希不過是傳聲筒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're Claire's words. Hennessey's just the mouthpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼文中還說我拒絕置評\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why does it say here that I declined to comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.95,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說過  會惹麻煩的事能躲就躲\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said you didn't want to kick up dust if we could avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是《紐約時代雜誌》  你應該告訴我的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's the New York fucking Times. You should've let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的決定  我承擔責任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That was my call. I'll take the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查明漢納希接下來會在哪裡出現\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Find out when Hennessey's next appearance is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要搞垮這個婊子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna beat this bitch down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道她針對你  但是針對她的話...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know she went after you, but going after her is --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是她  是克萊爾·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not her. Claire Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道加勒特可能會產生誤解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand how Garrett might misconstrue things,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟現在他壓力很大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}given the pressure he's under.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你肯定不會相信吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you can't honestly believe it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不知道該相信什麼了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to believe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯非常沮喪  他只是想幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis is devastated. All he wants to do is help,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.63,0:06:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他覺得自己受到了冤枉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but he feels like he's being unfairly accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想相信  克萊爾  但加勒特確信不疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to believe it, Claire, but Garrett is convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能跟他談談嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Will you talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我現在得集中精力維護我的家庭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have to concentrate on keeping my family together right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是跟他爭吵關於...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not getting into arguments over --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果弗蘭西斯真有什麼圖謀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If Francis were really up to something,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那他怎麼不直接把諮詢的事告訴鄧巴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}don't you think he would have told Dunbar about the therapy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他逼我們交出記錄就等於那麼做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He basically did by forcing us to hand over the logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你丈夫的決定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your husband chose to hand them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他拒絕  弗蘭西斯是不會逼他的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If he'd said no, Francis wouldn't have pressed the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟你爭這個  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to debate this with you, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只求你好好想想這件事  特莉莎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I'm asking is that you really think this through, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在跟你在一起嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is he with you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  只有我和你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. It's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要掛電話了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to get off the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你跟加勒特談談好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Will you please talk to Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得她會拋開丈夫站在我這邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't think she's going to side with me instead of her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了跟你  特莉莎還跟別人說過{\u1}阿普唑侖{\u0}的事嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did Tricia tell anyone else about the Xanax besides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}鎮靜抗焦慮藥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有  她對此非常敏感\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I doubt she would. She's very sensitive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要是跟別人說過  我們就可以把訊息傳出去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If she'd only told someone else, then we could just leak it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是這太明顯了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But it'll be too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醫生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.03,0:07:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在保護他們  他什麼都不會說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's protecting them. He won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非他們放棄保密特權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless they waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對他們可沒有好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They have absolutely nothing to gain by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是對我們有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得去見塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to meet with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我背叛了他  他為什麼還要見我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why would he talk to me after I back-stabbed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此他才會見你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's precisely why he'll talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能去聖路易斯  你知道的...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I can't go to St. Louis. You know --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克會來東部  你要做的就是找到他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tusk will come east. Your job is to get in the same room with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.64,0:08:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什麼計劃    -雷米·丹頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- What's the play?   - Remy Danton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去  讓杜蘭特來找我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go. Get me Durant, in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來安排\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  一定確保其他方面我們萬無一失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And Doug? Let's make sure we're airtight on everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能有軟肋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No Achilles heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.96,0:08:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"災難來臨了"  用混亂對抗混亂的人說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"Cry, 'Havoc,'" Said he who fought chaos with chaos,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"讓我們釋放戰爭惡魔"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"And let slip the dogs of war."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失約  數週不聯絡  你知道規矩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Missed appointments. No contact in weeks. You know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟格林特工談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to speak to Agent Green, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.94,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給格林打電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put Green on the fucking line, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你想說什麼  都可以跟我說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything you have to say, you can discuss it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要說的事遠遠超出了你的級別\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I have to say is way above your pay grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼關掉這破玩意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where do I turn off this shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看左邊的那塊螢幕\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look at the other screen, to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.57,0:09:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是美國電話電報公司八個資料中心的訪問網格\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That is the access grid to all eight of AT&T's data centers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你還是解開手銬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So what do you say you un-cuff me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後告訴格林特工我在等他的電話吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and tell Agent Green I'll be waiting for his call?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在試圖修復與中國的關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to repair relations with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給馮政治庇護就是一記耳光\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Giving Feng asylum would be a slap in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特有麻煩  他得表現出決心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Garrett's in trouble. He needs to appear resolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們的總統有多強  我們就有多強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're only as strong as the president we serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須拯救他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have to rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼能確定他的證詞不會扯上白宮\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How can you be sure his testimony won't implicate the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道誰有奶  誰是娘\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He knows where his bread is buttered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這不是要拯救總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This isn't about you saving the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-當然是    -這不是第一次了  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- Of course it is.   - We've been down this road before, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾·科恩  亞當·嘉樂威\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Michael Kern, Adam Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.32,0:09:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想當國務卿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to become secretary of state
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.40,0:09:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了進行有成效的外交\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in order to engage in productive diplomacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是全職損失控制\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}not full-time damage control.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們要讓加勒特回到正軌\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is why we have to put Garrett back on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想讓他脫軌吧  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want him on his ass, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是總統這麼跟你說的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is this what the president told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他現在太多疑了  凱茜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's paranoid, Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想讓大家跟我反目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He's trying to turn people against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.11,0:10:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你自己的行為讓大家跟你反目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're turning them against yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在要求我坑害總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're asking me to undermine the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假如總統對我的指責屬實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's say that what the President has accused me of is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就真的很糟嗎  考慮一下這麼做的結果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would that be so bad? If taken to its conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對你沒有好處嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't you stand to benefit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對國家沒有好處嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想牽扯進去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want anything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就再做一次  凱茜\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just one more time, Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別去管那些條條框框\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's unshackle ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.54,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次  馮先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is a one-time offer, Mr. Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要白紙黑字寫下來  不加任何條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would need it in writing. Open-ended, no restrictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法定豁免權也是一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The same goes for legal immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.81,0:10:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先我要確認\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}First I need to know whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否通過拉尼根的賭場洗錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you funneled money through Lanagin's casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  等我安全抵達美國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, no. I will speak freely once I've arrived safely
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才會全盤托出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你現在就能提供確鑿證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless you provide valuable evidence now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司法部長不會答應任何豁免權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the attorney general will not grant immunity on any level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在中國已經全部否認了這些指控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've denied these allegations in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的敵人想置我於死地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My enemies want me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是逼我給他們證據\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're asking me to give them confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為回報  我們會給你提供避難所\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And we're giving you safe haven in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在迪拜已經有避難所了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I already have safe haven in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡的庇護所只是暫時的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your asylum there is only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們給你提供的是永久身份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're offering you permanent status.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他們也會給我永久身份\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm confident that they will grant me permanent status.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是外交部長親口跟你說的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you hear that directly from the Minister of Foreign Affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛跟他談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I just spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你連護照都沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Right now you are a man without a passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北京方面還沒查封的資產\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever assets Beijing hasn't seized are frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也都被所有和中美關繫緊密的國家凍結了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in every country with close ties to the United Sates or China,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基本上是全世界所有國家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which is just about every country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要自由和金錢  我們想要資訊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want your freedom and fortune. We want information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我證實確實有洗錢行為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Confirm for me the existence of a money-laundering scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我們用賭場來掩飾外資流入\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes. We used the casino to mask foreign contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.05,0:12:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們中誰跟我講講這是怎麼回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One of you want to tell me what this is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必須得遵從\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.65,0:12:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說我得出席\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean I have to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非我們上訴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Unless we appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會輸\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'd lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她要不是證據確鑿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She wouldn't have issued the subpoena
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會傳喚我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}unless she had something substantial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什麼我覺得你該去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is why I think you should go
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並拒不解釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and plead the Fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得她手上有什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What do you think she has?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想妄加推斷\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to speculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天  我付給你們六個一天的錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}God damn it, I pay the six of you more in one day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比供個孩子上大學都多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}than it costs to put a kid through college.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我請你們是要你們比我知道得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I pay you to know more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她問詢時說的對我們會很有幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Her line of questioning will tell us a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一她真要提出指控  我們可以據此準備辯護\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can use that to prepare our defense in case there's an indictment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼時候走\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When do I have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的會面是在後天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your interview is the day after next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,48小時\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}48 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發動不了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Having trouble starting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  可能電池沒電了吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I think the battery might be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想試試跨接啟動  我有電線\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have some cables if you want to try and jump it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這真的不麻煩嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You sure you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你真是太好了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. It's really nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.64,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開引擎蓋  我把我車開過來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Pop your hood. I'll bring my car around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是彼得  他開車送我回來的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is Peter. He's the guy who drove me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些要放哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where do you want these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來拿  謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll take 'em. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瑞秋  是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rachel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麗薩說你倆是室友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lisa said you two were roommates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我給你拿點什麼  來杯水嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can I get you something? A glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  謝謝  我得走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, thanks. I should really get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  太謝謝你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All right. I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣  希望車能修好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My pleasure. Good luck with the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望只是電池沒電  晚安\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I hope it's only a dead battery. Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們應該給他些錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We should give him some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她得離開\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She needs to be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我說她可以留下的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Y-- you told me she could stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我改主意了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說你不在乎她在不在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you said you didn't care if she was here --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要解釋什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't need to explain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受不了了  是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't stand it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了我愛上了別人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The idea that I might actually love somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.21,0:14:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了我生命中除了你還有別人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That I might have somebody in my life who isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你在乎她  就讓她走  瑞秋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you care about her, make it happen, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  告訴你朋友我不會要錢的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah. You need to tell your friend that I won't take any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很樂意幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was happy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都需要好心人幫忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We all need a good Samaritan every now and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥金尼斯將軍被判處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you feel justice was served
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四十年有期徒刑時  你覺得正義得到伸張了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when General McGinnis got sentenced to 40 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}梅根·漢納希  反性侵活動分子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就他的罪行而言  正義是得以伸張了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, as far as his crimes go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還有成千的服役士兵沒有...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But not for thousands of servicemen and --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉打斷你的講話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm -- I'm sor-- I'm sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.14,0:15:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的製作人告訴我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}m-- my producer is telling me that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑奎琳·夏普剛打電話來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jacqueline Sharp has called in,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.83,0:15:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾議院多數黨黨鞭  議員女士  您在嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}the house majority whip. C-- congresswoman, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我在  克里斯  謝謝你接我的電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I'm here, Chris. And thank you for taking my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Hello, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議員女士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.03,0:15:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先  作為一名老兵\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}First of all, as a veteran like yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想感謝你對國家的貢獻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to thank you for your service to our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是責任  無需感謝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Duty doesn't require thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興你提到責任這個話題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm glad you brought up duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你最近將它稱之為洗腦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because you recently equated it with brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的本意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說"緊跟黨派路線"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said "Toeing the party line."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.58,0:15:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}電話連線  傑奎琳·夏普議員  眾議院多數黨黨鞭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的本意是文化和體系是...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I meant was that the culture and the system is one that --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是打電話來和你辯論的  梅根\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I didn't call to argue with you, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.67,0:15:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恰恰相反\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要解決這個問題  就必須找到共同點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't fix this problem until we find some common ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我來看這個問題沒有妥協空間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There is no middle ground as far as I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊需要改變\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The military needs to change --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我都曾經在軍中服役\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Can't we agree that you and I served
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以保護人民自由辯論的權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}so that we could protect open debate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這正是民主的基礎  你說不是嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which is the very bedrock of democracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理論上是的  但這不是我要說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, in theory, but that's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是理論上  是實際上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not in theory. In reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的人為了這份自由不惜犧牲生命\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Brave men and women die fighting for that freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的涵義就是為那些和你意見相左的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The meaning of bravery is fighting for the freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也同樣享有自由而戰鬥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}of those with whom you disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  但我們回到真正的話題上來好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Sure, but let's get back to the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為不勇敢的人是克萊爾·安德伍德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What I don't think is brave is Claire Underwood
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.64,0:16:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃避這場辯論  找你替她進行這場鬥爭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}dodging this debate and having you fight this battle for her instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我為什麼在和你而不是她談話  這是她的法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why am I talking to you instead of her? It's her bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是她  是我們共同的成果\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not just hers. It's all of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你勇敢地說出來了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Except one of you is brave enough to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而她卻是個懦夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and the other is a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安德伍德夫人勇敢地\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood was brave enough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在全國性電視節目上承認她...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to go on national television and admit that she --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但那之後她去哪了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and where has she been since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應付醜聞  躲避媒體\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Deflecting scandal and hiding from the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根  你在《紐約時代雜誌》上說我可恥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You called me disgraceful in The New York Times, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當然有這個權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you have every right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我也有權說  安德伍德夫人是可恥的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I also have the right to say that Mrs. Underwood is disgraceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because there is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比當逃兵更可恥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}more disgraceful than running from a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.51,0:16:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根  我們根本沒有...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Megan? That is -- we're not even...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上回來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去國會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮提到我或總統了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did Feng mention either me or the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴不肯說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dunbar wouldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但馮確認了洗錢行為\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But the fact that Feng confirmed the money laundering
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這足以讓白宮更受關注\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}increases focus on the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我們是清白的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, as long as we're innocent, which we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德·塔斯克被傳喚了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk has been subpoenaed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.39,0:17:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼找我們見面  比爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why did you ask for this meeting, Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.82,0:17:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就為了向我們通報訊息嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just keeping us in the loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你讓國務卿杜蘭特給予馮政治庇護嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you encourage Secretary Durant to offer Feng asylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.32,0:17:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比爾  我的天吶\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Bill, for god sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統也可能問我這個問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The president could have asked me that question himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為白宮顧問  這是我的責任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As the White House counsel, it is my responsibility --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這是杜蘭特自己的主意嘍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you're saying Durant acted of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道她的動機是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have no idea what her motivations were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和總統一樣感到震驚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just as shocked as the president
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她居然沒經過他本人允許就擅自而為了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that she would have gone through with this without his direct approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個問題我想和你談談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's another matter I'd like to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以  最好只跟你談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Privately, if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們單獨待會兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just give us a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-諮詢    -是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- The therapy.- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,具體說  就是放棄保密權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}To be specific, the confidentiality waiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮的證詞把我們推到一個非常尷尬的位置上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feng's testimony puts us in a very awkward position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在面對放棄保密權的極大壓力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're under a great deal of pressure to waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不放棄  就相當於總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we don't, it implies that the president
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承認了他沒做過的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}may have confessed to things he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.71,0:18:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴只是在瞎猜  別讓步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dunbar is just grasping. Don't give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但拉金宗教指導保密協議的說法並不可靠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But Larkin's argument for spiritual confidentiality is shaky at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想控制事態的發展\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We want to control how this thing plays out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能幫什麼忙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要確保不會再節外生枝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to know if anyone else might pop out of the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒對任何人說過  克萊爾也沒說過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I haven't mentioned it to anyone, and neither has Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會辜負總統對我的信任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I would never betray the president's trust like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你抽出時間\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴總統  我非常難過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tell the president it saddens me that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在只能通過律師交流\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we now have to communicate through lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是他想親自\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I will make myself available
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我談談  我會抽出時間的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if he wants to discuss any of this in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅根的話太過分了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What Megan said was offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不該質疑你的品行\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She shouldn't have questioned your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那都是精心準備的談話要點  而且不是她準備的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Those were talking points. Carefully crafted, and not by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:19:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是來挑釁的  傑姬  我是來解決問題的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not here to pick a fight, Jackie. I'm here to end one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要法案進行投票  這事就會結束\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it'll end soon enough when the bill goes to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會進行投票的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It won't go to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟艾琳·布魯克斯談過了  我要撤銷法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've spoken to Elaine Brooks and I'm withdrawing the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.07,0:19:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的有一定道理\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What you said had some truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前你提出\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And early on you offered
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起找個折中的辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to sit down with me and find a middle ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那時拒絕了你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I decided to draw a line in the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但勇敢的做法應該是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And the braver thing would've been for me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收起我的驕傲  跟你好好談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to swallow my pride and sit down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還願談  我想重新開始\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're still open to that, I'd love to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.71,0:19:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和弗蘭克在打什麼主意嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Are you and Frank up to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一項能通過的法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A passable bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他讓南茜監視我  他把我的個人生活搞得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He had Nancy spy on me. He brought my personal life into --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯習慣了事事得逞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Francis is used to getting his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會不惜一切確保成功\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he'll do anything to make sure he does,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是對我重要的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}especially if it's something important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  克萊爾  我很懷疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know, Claire. I'm skeptical.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前那樣對待你  我們深表歉意\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're deeply sorry for the way we've treated you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們想重拾失去的信任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and we want to rebuild the trust we've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得這可能嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you think that's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉突然這麼來了  我打過電話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to ambush you. I tried calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能這麼對我  克萊爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't do this to me, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說得很清楚  我必須尊重加勒特的意願\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was very clear that I have to respect Garrett's wishes --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個  是性侵犯法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not that. The sexual assault bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會進行投票了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not going to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,議長從日程中刪除了嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did the speaker remove it from the docket?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是我撤掉了  我剛跟傑姬談過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I did. I just spoke to Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為她那樣說你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is because of what she said about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我主要是擔心她接下來會不會對付你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My main concern is that she doesn't come after you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和加勒特接受調查期間絕不能發生這種事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not while you and Garrett are going through the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想來告訴你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought you should be aware
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.34,0:20:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我知道這項法案對你有多重要\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because I know how much this bill meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為法案投入了那麼多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All the work you've put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都投入過  但我們要通過傑姬的法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That we've put in. But we'll pass Jackie's version,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,邁出這一小步  循序漸進\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}take this baby step, and build on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.88,0:20:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法案的事我很失望\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm disappointed about the bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不得不說  我鬆了口氣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I have to say, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說凱瑟琳做了什麼嗎  許諾馮政治避難\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you hear what Catherine did? Giving Feng asylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加勒特氣瘋了  他覺得走投無路\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Garrett's beside himself. He feels cornered,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下我們除了放棄保密權別無選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}like we have no choice but to waive the privileges now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藥物的事呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But what about the medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是啊  我不該說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know. I shouldn't be sharing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說了  你該走了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We don't have to talk about it. You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你日程排得很滿\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know you have a packed schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這麼做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在走廊裡單獨找上了她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I had to do was get her alone in a hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說傑姬那邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I meant with Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要分清輕重緩急\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have our priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道做這樣的放棄並不容易\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, I know it isn't easy to let go of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答應我一件事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Promise me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.15,0:21:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能一個人住在這房子裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't live in this house alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是這麼說  但這事可能事與願違\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You say that, but this could all backfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德肯定會拒不解釋\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond will plead the Fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他提到我  便是承認有罪了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If he names me, it's an admission of his own wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我更擔心加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm more worried about Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你製造了一個有力的對手\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You've made a powerful enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們比他們強\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're stronger than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可他仍然是總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And he's still the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保證  你被迫做出的一切犧牲之中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I promise you, of all of the sacrifices that you've had to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會包括與一名罪犯離婚\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}divorcing a convict will not be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能放棄保密權  加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can't waive the privileges, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.60,0:22:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒別的選擇了  馮承認了那筆錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't have a choice anymore. Feng confirmed the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.87,0:22:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在電話上承認的  不是當面正式承認的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Over the phone. Not in a formal interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,解除對他的庇護  送他回去\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Rescind the asylum. Send him back --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妨礙司法公正\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Obstruction of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉利克這麼說的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Is that what Galich said?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人肯定會這麼想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Definitely how it would be perceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.61,0:22:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們任何不配合調查的舉動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And anything we do that looks like a failure to cooperate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都會加重他們的猜疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}amplifies that perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是不想公開我們的婚姻問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I just don't want our marriage put on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴會問我是否提及過中國  我沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Look, Dunbar'll ask if I brought up China. I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.58,0:22:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉金能證明我的清白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So Larkin can only help to exonerate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果婚姻諮詢最終進入報告  也無所謂\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if the marriage counseling ends up in the report, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.58,0:22:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們能渡過這個難關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We can survive that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.68,0:22:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他給我們開了處方藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he prescribed us medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不算是我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Technically not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在吃我的藥  加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You took mine, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.25,0:22:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉金知道你會吃才給我開的藥\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Larkin wrote the prescription to me knowing you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你提過了  處方藥的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, have you mentioned it? The medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟克萊爾嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我只能跟她傾訴\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. But she's the only person I can talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有她能理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who really understands what it's like --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們更要放棄保密權了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, all the more reason we have to waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.84,0:22:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們洩露出去  就由不得我們做主了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If they leak this, we can't control the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.66,0:22:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾不會那麼做的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看她\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't underestimate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.41,0:22:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要是真準備這麼做  現在不早做了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If they were going to, don't you think they would have done it by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.44,0:23:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她為了減少我們的負擔  放棄了性侵法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She dropped the sexual assault bill to reduce pressure on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也許是這麼跟你說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That may have been what she told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們什麼都不會說的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're not going to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.72,0:23:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求你了  加勒特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm begging you, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.42,0:23:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄保密權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們談論的事太私密了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The things we talked about were so intimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.06,0:23:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果孩子們看到\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Imagine if the kids --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.14,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但是特莉莎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I know. But Tricia --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們競選的時候\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}When we ran,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我們的生活將被人仔細審視\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I knew every aspect of our lives would be under scrutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.12,0:23:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得我們至少還能保護這個\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I thought we could protect at least this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.79,0:23:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生在這裡的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What happens in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會不惜一切保護我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll protect us. Whatever I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要相信我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們檢查了USB軟體狗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We checked the USB dongle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.17,0:24:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聲稱感染了資訊中心的程式碼不在裡面\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The code you're claiming infected the data center isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.14,0:24:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我設計那段程式碼一到達伺服器便自我刪除\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I programmed the code to self-erase as soon as it hit the server.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.94,0:24:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在盧卡斯被捕之前就不見了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was gone before Lucas was in cuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你信不過我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.06,0:24:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可是世上最複雜的防火牆之一\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is one of the most sophisticated firewalls in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.45,0:24:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算真的進去了  也破壞不了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Even if your code did get in there, you couldn't break it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.95,0:24:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子手機的運營商就是他們公司\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your wife uses AT&T.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.89,0:24:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她情人也是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So does her lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.45,0:24:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她現在就在那兒  喬納森·坎普\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's over there right now. Jonathan Kemp.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.95,0:24:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的脊椎按摩師  對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's her chiropractor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.44,0:24:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想看看他們互發的簡訊嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Want to see their texts to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.58,0:24:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.04,0:24:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你早就知道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, I see you already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.17,0:24:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解你不想把事情鬧大\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't blame you for not making a fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.56,0:24:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟孩子們還在家裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what with the kids still at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.42,0:24:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你讓我的程式碼進了那扇門\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you walked my code right through that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.64,0:24:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進入了三千兩百萬人的手機裡\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Into 32 million people's phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.65,0:24:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都怪你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And that's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.51,0:24:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聯調局也罪責難逃  這會鬧得很難看\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it's on the FBI. And it is a shit-storm
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.21,0:25:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓聯調局面臨國會的調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that will bring the Bureau right in front of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.17,0:25:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你告訴我  平息這一切要多大代價\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you tell me: How much is making that disappear worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.38,0:25:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你面臨一百年的監禁\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have a hundred years hanging over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.75,0:25:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敲詐聯調局對你沒好處\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Extorting the FBI won't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.47,0:25:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是道格拉斯·斯坦普讓你陷害盧卡斯·古德溫的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did Douglas Stamper tell you to set up Lucas Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.50,0:25:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反恐主管\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Counter-Terrorism Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.65,0:25:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟白宮聯絡官相比真是一步登天\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a big step up from White House Liaison.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.54,0:25:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我認為你背後有推手    -胡說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- I think you had a helping hand.   - Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.46,0:25:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續編  但以下是我的要求\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Keep lying. Meanwhile, here's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.77,0:25:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一  我不再是你的走狗了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}One, I'm no longer your bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.07,0:25:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二  撤銷對我的所有指控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Two, all of my charges are dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.25,0:25:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三  撤銷所有對巴利特·布朗的指控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Three, all of Barrett Brown's charges are dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.44,0:25:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這得看聯邦檢察官的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's up to the U.S. Attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.66,0:25:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去想辦法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.49,0:25:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我聽得沒錯\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I'm hearing you correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.41,0:25:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是想要拉金的證詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}you'd like to keep Larkin's testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.18,0:25:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,側重在洗錢上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}focused on the money laundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.42,0:25:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我從來沒提過  因為我毫不知情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which I never brought up, because I knew nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.29,0:25:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你擔心其他的事  私人的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But your concern is other matters. Private matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.40,0:25:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些和調查無關\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which are irrelevant to the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.08,0:25:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能阻止鄧巴問問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't prevent Dunbar from asking what she's gonna ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.36,0:25:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然不能\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.60,0:25:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最多只能去拜托拉金博士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The most I can do is ask Dr. Larkin
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.20,0:25:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他對下部分問題的回答\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}how he would respond to certain questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.42,0:26:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他很聰明  會明白我的目的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he's a smart man. He'll understand what I'm getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.66,0:26:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這路子合法嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this approach keeps us within the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.40,0:26:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有干擾證詞嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're not tampering with testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.64,0:26:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,界線很模糊  但我會確保合法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's a fine line. But I'll stay on the right side of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.96,0:26:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不見我  弗蘭克  就像他對你一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He shut me out, Frank. Just like he did with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.85,0:26:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的副國務卿被委派了全權外交權\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My undersecretary has been assigned full diplomatic authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.07,0:26:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時的挫折  凱茜  我到哪你到哪\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A temporary setback, Cathy. Where I go, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.02,0:26:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在總統正在戰況室\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}At this very moment, the President is in the Situation Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.41,0:26:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中方對馮的政治庇護的反應跟我預想的一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}China responded to Feng's asylum exactly the way I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.30,0:26:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們增派了一倍海軍前往與那國島\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're doubling their naval presence off the coast of Yonaguni.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.11,0:26:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你猜誰被趕出戰況室了  你和我  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And you know who isn't in the Situation Room? You and I, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.45,0:26:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只盯著眼下一時的得失\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're thinking about where we are
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.02,0:26:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻對情勢的發展方向視而不見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}instead of where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.56,0:26:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不像那個在傑斐遜舞會上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now that isn't the Catherine Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.48,0:26:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我共舞華爾茲的凱瑟琳·杜蘭特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that I waltzed with at the Jefferson Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.92,0:26:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她深明大勢所趨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She understood potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.87,0:26:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她盯著未來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She had her eyes toward the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.97,0:26:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對那個凱瑟琳·杜蘭特說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I told that Catherine Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.64,0:26:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要她這樣的人領導國務院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that we needed her in the State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.43,0:27:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是如此  真不知她哪去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We still need her. I wish I knew where she was,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.36,0:27:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她和我眼前這個凱瑟琳·杜蘭特\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because she is not the Catherine Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.35,0:27:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全是兩種人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}sitting in front of me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.35,0:27:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我跟你說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I'll tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.47,0:27:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果她不趕快回來的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If she doesn't show up soon, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.39,0:27:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那這支華爾茲  我只好獨自舞下去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm just gonna have to keep waltzing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.66,0:27:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because I am done trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.91,0:27:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想再去說服我面前的這個女人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}convince this woman in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.92,0:27:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我攜手前行了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to take my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.68,0:27:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快忙去吧  我不留你了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, don't let me keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.74,0:27:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這兒  我哪也不去  弗蘭克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm here. I'm not going anywhere, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.22,0:27:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在能拿到總統簡報嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You still have access to the presidential briefing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.33,0:27:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能  就在我手上\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Yes, I have it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.23,0:27:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說說與中國之間的全部情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Walk me through everything that's going on with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.83,0:27:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮也出場了  也許我們用得上他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feng is in play now. We might be able to use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.75,0:27:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼用\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.52,0:27:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還不知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.21,0:27:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但顯然他在北京眼裡是有價值的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But he's clearly valuable to Beijing,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.54,0:27:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼他對我們就也有價值\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}which makes him valuable to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.01,0:27:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從沒提起過馮山德嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing about Xander Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.16,0:28:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.94,0:28:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼爾·拉尼根呢  還有雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Daniel Lanagin? Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.00,0:28:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只談了他的婚姻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We only discussed their marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.58,0:28:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從未涉及白宮的公務\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Nothing about the business of the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.10,0:28:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可曾間接提起過與工作有關的壓力\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Any oblique reference to work-related pressures he was feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他現在睡眠太少\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He said he wasn't getting as much sleep as he'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.25,0:28:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給他開過什麼藥物嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you ever prescribe him any medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.11,0:28:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如我一貫聲稱  我只提供宗教諮詢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As I've always stated, I provided religious counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.00,0:28:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  但我問的是藥物處方\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I understand. But I'm asking about medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.83,0:28:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼關係嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How is this relevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.05,0:28:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想查證他的判斷力是否因此受影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to assess whether his judgment may have been impaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.97,0:28:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來  他和他的妻子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In my opinion, he and his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.19,0:28:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對的是典型的婚姻問題\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}were dealing with standard marital issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.41,0:28:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是答非所問  拉金博士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's not what I asked, Dr. Larkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.96,0:28:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我再問第三遍\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So I will ask for a third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.38,0:28:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且問得更明確些\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And let me be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.50,0:28:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美利堅合眾國總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Was any medication prescribed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.06,0:28:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在接受你的諮詢服務時  你是否提供過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}or taken as a result of your counseling session
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.63,0:28:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何形式的處方或者藥物\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by the President of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.86,0:28:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的工作能力完全沒有受影響\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His faculties were operating at a hundred percent,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.26,0:28:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是想問這個的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}if that's what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.50,0:28:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有政府方面的人和你談過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Has anyone from the administration spoken to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.01,0:28:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.87,0:29:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於取證  是不是有人找過你  指導過你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}About this deposition. Has anyone approached you, coached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.59,0:29:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你現在承認  我會將此認定為及時申報\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you tell me now, I will qualify that as a timely declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.42,0:29:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想繼續了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.09,0:29:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統放棄了他的保密權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The President waived his privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.63,0:29:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我是自願作證的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But I'm here voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.33,0:29:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉金博士  一開始你不肯作證\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Dr. Larkin, at first you wouldn't talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.64,0:29:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那有違你的道德準則\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}because it violated your ethical code.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.31,0:29:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我尊重你的選擇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.36,0:29:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我要問你  作為一個虔誠之人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But let me ask you, as a man of faith
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.50,0:29:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓄意對我說謊  難道就不違反你的道德準則嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is deliberately lying to me an exception to that code?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.30,0:29:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你拒絕說出實情的話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because that is what you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.91,0:29:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就有作偽證的嫌疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by refusing to share the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.19,0:29:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.82,0:29:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這法案過不了的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It wasn't going to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.69,0:29:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你說我們就要爭取到足夠的支援了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you said we almost had the votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.75,0:29:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要能完全確定  但實情並非如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We needed to be a hundred percent solid, and we weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.83,0:29:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果法案未能通過  我們的努力就白費了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the bill failed, that would set us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.29,0:29:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須接受漸進的改革方案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We need to accept incremental reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.66,0:29:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的口氣跟傑姬·夏普一模一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You sound just like Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.38,0:29:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我現在與她合作了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm actually working with her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.69,0:29:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是一個有力的盟友\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}She's a powerful ally for us to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.01,0:29:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可她那樣讓我下不來臺\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}After what she did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.78,0:29:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還公開羞辱你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}After what she said about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.86,0:30:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要是被他人的非議所左右\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If I let the things people say about me get under my skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.71,0:30:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我連家門都出不去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't be able to leave my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.14,0:30:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道結果會怎樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You know how this will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.27,0:30:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人人都會說"太好了  我們取得了成功"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everyone will say, "Great, we did something,"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.80,0:30:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其實一無所成\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Which is really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.50,0:30:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會高興一時  然後就拋諸腦後忘個乾淨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They'll pat themselves on the back and they'll forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.89,0:30:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們讓人們注意這個話題了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We helped put this on the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.09,0:30:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我們是要真正改變現狀\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought we were doing something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.44,0:30:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,改變人們的生活  幼稚死了  對吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Changing people's lives. How naive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.98,0:30:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但至少我不願意放棄\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But at least I didn't want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.19,0:30:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許傑姬·夏普說對了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Maybe Jackie Sharp is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.00,0:30:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽就是個懦夫\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are a fucking coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.41,0:30:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我鼓勵你站出來說出你的遭遇\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm the one that pulled you out from under the covers.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.63,0:30:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前你在逃避  靠吃藥度日\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You were hiding. You and your pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.35,0:30:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,編造各種謊言自欺欺人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So you tell yourself whatever you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.31,0:30:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失態了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.79,0:30:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些政治現實  是我們無法忽視的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There were political realities we couldn't ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.94,0:30:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想沒想過為什麼那麼多人憎恨華盛頓\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you ever wonder why so many people hate Washington?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.19,0:30:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為你這種人說那種屁話\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's because of people like you using phrases like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.21,0:31:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.50,0:31:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說該開燈  但既然花錢住進\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd turn the lights on, but when you're paying for the room
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.31,0:31:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風景最好的房間  就不如欣賞個夠\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}with the best view you might as well make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.16,0:31:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒上過頂層  你呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've never been in the penthouse here. Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.32,0:31:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼情況\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.51,0:31:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我為什麼來華盛頓嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you know why I'm in D.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.54,0:31:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's okay, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.90,0:31:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能說出的話我都已經知道了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's nothing you can say that I don't already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.65,0:31:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮要去作證了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Feng is on his way to testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.52,0:31:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管賽斯跟你說了什麼都不要信他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever Seth has told you, don't believe a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.59,0:31:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會說什麼我不該相信的事呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What might he have told me that I shouldn't believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.91,0:31:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟副總統見面了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You met with the Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.79,0:31:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一座教堂裡  別裝作沒這回事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In a church. Don't pretend you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.21,0:31:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想當牆頭草嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Playing both sides?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.51,0:31:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  我...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond, look --
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.14,0:31:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想聽你說出來  你跟弗蘭克見面了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I want to hear you say it. That you met with Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.17,0:31:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟你說的  雷蒙德  但他不能在這兒\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to you, Raymond, but not with him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.09,0:31:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先出去吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.21,0:31:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我在電梯裡等你嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Should I hold the elevator for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.44,0:31:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾你媽的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Go fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.12,0:31:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  那你走樓梯吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Okay. You can take the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.84,0:32:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在耍你  雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They're toying with you, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.31,0:32:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  但是你也一樣  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No doubt. But so are you, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.04,0:32:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是想哄騙弗蘭克  讓他以為已經安全了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I wanted to lead Frank on, give him a false sense of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.65,0:32:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要說謊  那就說得漂亮點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If you're gonna lie, lie better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.87,0:32:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想離間我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}They want to tear us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.75,0:32:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要多條退路  這我不怪你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't blame you for wanting to keep your options open.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.66,0:32:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你顯然買錯了保險\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But clearly you have bought the wrong insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.49,0:32:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣搬起石頭砸自己的腳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Don't shoot yourself in the foot like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.60,0:32:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳  石頭也是你拿著呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Your foot. And you're holding the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.42,0:32:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找個別的地方流血吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now go someplace else to bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.57,0:32:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想談談流血嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want to talk about blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.88,0:32:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你與弗蘭克的這場戰爭已經讓你流了多少血了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How much have you spilt in this war with Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.48,0:32:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做的一切都是為了維護和平\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All I've tried to do is keep the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.55,0:32:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本可讓他佔上風\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You could've let him have the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.04,0:32:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了你的自尊  還會讓你損失什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What would that have really cost you, other than your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.65,0:32:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Such a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.27,0:32:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛樹立了身家420億的敵人  雷米\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You have just made 42 billion enemies, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.22,0:33:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外加一些零頭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And some change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.52,0:33:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,390億  雷蒙德  你的市值在縮水\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}39 billion, Raymond. Your market cap is shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.30,0:33:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮顧問比爾·嘉利克今早被特別檢查官\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}White House Counsel Bill Galich was called into questioning this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.95,0:33:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}比爾·嘉利克
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.42,0:33:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希瑟·鄧巴傳喚質詢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}by Special Prosecutor Heather Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.78,0:33:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從鄧巴辦公室得到的訊息稱\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}According to Dunbar's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.46,0:33:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們懷疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}there are suspicions that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.12,0:33:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉利克可能干預了證人證詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Galich may have tampered with witness testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.99,0:33:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這名證人是托馬斯·拉金博士\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The witness in question is Dr. Thomas Larkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.77,0:33:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一位牧師與諮詢師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}a reverend and therapist
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.17,0:33:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據稱他為總統和第一夫人進行了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}who allegedly conducted secret marriage counseling sessions
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.09,0:33:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祕密婚姻諮詢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}for the president and first lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.36,0:33:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有來自總統的明確指示\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The White House counsel wouldn't be manipulating testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮顧問是不會去干預證詞的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}without explicit direction from the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.20,0:33:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同樣讓人不安的是  我們的總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And just as disconcerting is the fact that our president
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.44,0:33:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在尋求心理治療\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}is seeking psychological treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.98,0:33:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並且向美國人民隱瞞這一點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and chose to hide this from the American people.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.96,0:33:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果在這方面我們無法信任他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If we can't trust him about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.10,0:33:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們又怎麼知道他是否與洗錢陰謀有關呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}then how do we know he wasn't involved in a money-laundering scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.19,0:33:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼知道他的精神狀況適合來領導我們呢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How do we know he's mentally fit to lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.56,0:33:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是  如果他知法犯法\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And most important, how can he enforce the law
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.73,0:33:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又如何維護法律\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}when he's breaking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.86,0:33:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為我們眾議院的同事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I believe our colleagues in the House certainly have enough
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.81,0:33:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經有足夠理由考慮彈劾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to consider Articles of Impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.52,0:33:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信任與法律都被踐踏\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Both trust and laws have been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.95,0:34:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管眾議院作何打算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Whatever the House decides to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.28,0:34:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位總統必須承擔責任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we must hold this president accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.45,0:34:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全力支援總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Fully support the president
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.42,0:34:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼都跟他站在一起\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and will stand by him no matter what comes his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.43,0:34:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攬進來  處理掉  給我找艾拉·薩伊德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Put that in, put it out. Then get me Ayla Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.44,0:34:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於雷米  讓他再多倒黴一陣子吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And as for Remy, let's let him wither on the vine a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.69,0:34:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時  讓他的另一半明天來眾議院\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, have his better half come by the house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.53,0:34:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.75,0:34:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.37,0:34:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.52,0:34:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鄧巴女士  我活了67年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, Ms. Dunbar, in 67 years on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.61,0:34:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還從來沒被傳喚過\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have never once been issued a subpoena.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.70,0:34:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在總算可以從遺願清單上劃掉了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can now cross that off my bucket list.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.56,0:34:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此次會面將被記錄和封存\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This interview is being recorded and sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.99,0:34:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如傳票所述  塔斯克先生  我與馮山德談過了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}As the subpoena mentioned, Mr. Tusk, I spoke with Xander Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.51,0:35:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他指證你與他合作  自2005年以來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}He verified that you were his partner
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.26,0:35:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將中國資金洗白並流入超級政治行動委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}in laundering Chinese money to political Super PACs since 2005.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.14,0:35:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你如何迴應他的指控\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}How would you respond to his allegations?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.10,0:35:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的客戶要行使憲法第五修正案賦予的權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My client exercises his right to plead the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.81,0:35:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是否曾用這些捐贈來換取政治利益\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you ever use these contributions to bargain for political favors?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.34,0:35:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的客戶要行使憲法第五修正案賦予的權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My client exercises his right to plead the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.58,0:35:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟丹尼爾·拉尼根是什麼關係\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What was your relationship with Daniel Lanagin?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.76,0:35:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的客戶要行使憲法第五修正案賦予的權利\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My client exercises his right to plead the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.73,0:35:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都記不得我為什麼要來這兒了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't even remember why I came over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.53,0:35:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說你最初來我家嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean when you first showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.44,0:35:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我是說來廚房\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. To the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.17,0:35:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉  別認為我不愛你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. Please don't think that I don't love you --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.82,0:35:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是為什麼  我不明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Then why? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.24,0:35:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切發展得太快了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything's been so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.26,0:35:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.87,0:36:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  很難說清  但我還沒準備好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't know. It's hard to explain, but I'm not ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.02,0:36:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-都是胡說    -不是的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- That's bullshit.   - No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.22,0:36:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還在努力適應新生活\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm still trying to figure out this new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.63,0:36:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一切太讓人搞不清\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And this is too confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.17,0:36:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有這是清清楚楚的  這你知道\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}This is the only thing that's clear, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.98,0:36:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在害怕  但這是好事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're afraid, but it's good to be afraid when you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.47,0:36:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得離開  為了你自己好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I need you to leave, okay? For your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.21,0:36:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只會傷害你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I am just gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.68,0:36:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我比你想得堅韌得多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have thicker skin than you can even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.29,0:36:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把事情搞得太痛苦\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Please don't make this harder than it has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.46,0:36:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天一切都還好好的  這麼突然\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Everything was fine yesterday. It's so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.47,0:36:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡直莫名其妙\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's like it's coming out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.75,0:36:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣  我已經考慮了一段時間了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not. I've been thinking about it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.98,0:36:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有  否則我會察覺的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No, you haven't. I would have sensed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.62,0:36:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能請你  拜託你走就是了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Would you please, please, please just go?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.28,0:36:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我發生了什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.90,0:36:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不指望你會理解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't expect you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.02,0:36:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許你可以試著...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe if you try --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.92,0:36:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓你待在這兒  好嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't want you here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.23,0:36:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不像你愛我那樣愛著你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't love you the way that you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.35,0:36:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是利用你  因為有你陪著感覺很好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I was using you because it felt good to have you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.05,0:36:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那樣很自私\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but it was selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.63,0:36:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說那些話  因為我知道你愛聽\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said the words because I knew you wanted to hear 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.92,0:36:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是真心的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but I didn't mean 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.71,0:36:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想繼續說下去了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I don't want to keep saying 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.47,0:36:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出去走一會兒  你收拾東西吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go for a walk while you pack your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.16,0:37:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不要這兒的任何東西\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}No. I don't want anything that's been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.74,0:37:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麗薩\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Lisa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.53,0:37:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"四面的山窪霧氣氤氳\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}"There was a steaming mist in all the hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.20,0:37:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淒涼地往山頂湧動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and it roamed in its forlornness up the hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.32,0:37:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}雙城記
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.67,0:37:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿是個邪惡的精靈  尋找歇腳之地而不得\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}like an evil spirit, seeking rest and finding none.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.77,0:37:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那霧粘乎乎的  冰寒徹骨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A clammy, and intensely cold mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.18,0:37:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緩緩地在空中波浪式地翻滾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it made it its slow way through the air in ripples
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.34,0:37:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一浪一浪清晰可見  然後宛如汙濁的海濤\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that visibly followed and overspread one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.95,0:37:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.88,0:37:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此滲誘  融合成了一片\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}as the waves of an unwholesome sea might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.31,0:37:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,霧很濃  車燈幾乎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It was dense enough to shut out everything
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.64,0:37:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也照不見"\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}from the light of the coach lamps."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.91,0:37:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很驚訝你想和我聊聊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised you wanted to speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.98,0:38:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是很受政府歡迎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I haven't been the biggest friend of the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.86,0:38:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道不是找你談話的最佳理由嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Isn't that the very best reason to speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.64,0:38:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想開始錄音\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'd like to begin recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.97,0:38:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請便\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.11,0:38:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,許多政治分析家預測\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}A number of political analysts predict
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.97,0:38:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眾議院司法委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}that the House Judiciary Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.34,0:38:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將就彈劾條款開始聽證會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}will commence with hearings on Articles of Impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.75,0:38:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先就此打住\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Let's just stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.27,0:38:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的這些分析家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}So these analysts you speak of,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.10,0:38:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在鄧巴的報告發表前就做出預測\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}they're making predictions prior to Dunbar's report even being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.12,0:38:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告出來可能得好幾個月\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That could take months.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.17,0:38:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,司法委員會絕不會等那麼久的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's no way the Judiciary will sit on this for that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.60,0:38:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是聽證會的根本問題嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And isn't that the fundamental flaw with these hearings?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.58,0:38:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為包括你在內的媒體記者提出的假設\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The committee feels compelled to act because of hypotheses
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.97,0:38:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委員會覺得必須採取行動\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}advanced by those in the media, such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.94,0:38:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能代表我所有的同行  但我只是報導事實\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't speak for all of my colleagues, but I'm just reporting facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.57,0:38:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可能會說這是事實  但實話說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, you may call them facts, but if we're being honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.84,0:38:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-難道不是    -每篇文章和採訪中\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- aren't they just --   - In every article and interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.01,0:38:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都只是提出懷疑\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I report alleged activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.09,0:38:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑重複的次數夠多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And if you repeat allegations enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.17,0:38:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一遍一遍  反反覆覆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}again and over and over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.10,0:38:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就三人成虎了  這是人之常情\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}people start to believe that they're true. That's human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.44,0:38:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做過調查\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I've done my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.60,0:39:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馮山德已經承認洗錢\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Xander Feng admitted to the money laundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.45,0:39:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你已經不報導馮山德了  對嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But you're no longer writing about Xander Feng. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.81,0:39:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你現在報導政府\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You're writing about the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.62,0:39:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實上  聽證會就是由媒體報導引發的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The truth is, these hearings have been initiated by the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.74,0:39:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我擔心的是總統會遭到媒體的審判\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And my fear is that the president will be tried by the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.02,0:39:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信他是無罪的嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Do you believe he's innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.06,0:39:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕對\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.90,0:39:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在書面聲明中這麼寫  我現在也還要這麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I said so in my written statement and I say so again now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.19,0:39:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白宮的法律顧問已經否認了干預拉金博士的證詞\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The White House counsel has denied coaching Dr. Larkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.49,0:39:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-但根據...    -不管最終發現了什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}- but according to Ms. --   - Whatever comes to light,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.35,0:39:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都只會證明總統的清白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}it will only prove the president's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.50,0:39:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你為什麼  加勒特·沃克是我所認識的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And I'll tell you why. I have never known anyone more honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.74,0:39:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最誠實  正直  愛國的人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}ethical, and patriotic than Garrett Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.25,0:39:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他對我國憲法和法律的尊重\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}His reverence for the Constitution and the laws of this country
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.85,0:39:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無人能及\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}are surpassed by none.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.77,0:39:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特莉莎和我有幸擁有一段堅固忠誠的婚姻\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Tricia and I have been blessed with a strong and loving marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.55,0:39:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但再堅固的婚姻也會面臨挑戰\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But even strong marriages face challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.30,0:39:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像成百萬的美國人一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Like millions of Americans,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.42,0:39:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們向一位宗教導師尋求建議\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we sought counseling from a spiritual advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.10,0:39:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他恰好也是一位職業治療師\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}one who happened also to be a professional therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.08,0:39:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多年來我們經常\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Over the years we have often
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.60,0:39:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在困境中向我們的信仰尋求幫助\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}turned to our faith in times of adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.69,0:40:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多人批評我們\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Many have criticized us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.87,0:40:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你們寧願要一位不去尋求幫助的總統嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But would you rather have a president that doesn't ask for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.59,0:40:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每一天都會請我妻子幫我\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I ask for help from my wife every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.79,0:40:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們相扶相依已經有23年了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've relied on one another for 23 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.42,0:40:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起養育了兩個漂亮的孩子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We've raised two beautiful children together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.68,0:40:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑體簡體\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}華爾街電訊報  副總統維護總統
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.62,0:40:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起走過了競選之旅\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Endured the campaign trails together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.87,0:40:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從州首府丹佛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}From the state capital in Denver
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.95,0:40:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路來到國家首都\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to the nation's capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.70,0:40:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直都在彼此身邊\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we've always been at each other's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.11,0:40:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嫁給這個人的原因\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I married this man for the
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.03,0:40:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你們很多人選他的原因一樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}same reason that so many of you voted for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.92,0:40:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是一位信徒  因為他熱愛家人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because he's a man of God. Because he believes in family.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.19,0:40:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他有同情心和愛心\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because he is compassionate and loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.69,0:40:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人無完人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Now, none of us are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.97,0:40:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是  特莉莎也不是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not. Tricia's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.04,0:40:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,儘管她很接近完美了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Although she certainly comes close.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.92,0:40:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  馮先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good morning, Mr. Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.28,0:40:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會否認我作為凡人的極限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I won't ignore what makes me human.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.85,0:40:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否則只是盲目\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's a form of blindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.83,0:40:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的領導者應該正視自己的缺點\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Good leadership means tackling my imperfections head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.17,0:40:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對一個在逃亡的人來說不錯嘛\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not bad for a man on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.50,0:40:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說對一個有豁免權的人來說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You mean a man with immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.76,0:41:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你想怎麼說了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Wherever you're most comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.50,0:41:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有很多事要談\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have a lot to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.07,0:41:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在瞭解情況的前提下這麼做的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I do so with open eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.36,0:41:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的愛也是明明白白的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just as I love, with open eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.68,0:41:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛我的妻子  愛上帝\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}my wife, my maker,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.27,0:41:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛我的國家\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.11,0:41:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.36,0:41:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  密查姆\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.70,0:41:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬  一般來說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jackie, in these circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.81,0:41:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會去找你\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}normally I would come to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.46,0:41:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我們還是保持距離為好\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}but we need to keep a public distance for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.87,0:41:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以為我是來討論性侵法案的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I thought I was here to discuss the sexual assault bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.95,0:41:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  還有其他的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You are. Among other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.85,0:41:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.06,0:41:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有條件\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}There's a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.55,0:41:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.51,0:41:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管今天你說什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm going to support your bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.84,0:41:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都會支援你的法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}no matter what you say today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.99,0:41:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Regarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.23,0:41:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彈劾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.53,0:41:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果事情真鬧到司法委員會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Well, if it goes to the Judiciary --
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.31,0:42:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎肯定是會的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It most definitely will.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.44,0:42:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不那麼肯定\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.94,0:42:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們看了總統的聲明瞭嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Did you see the president's address?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.44,0:42:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們看了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.24,0:42:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得能起些作用  控制事態\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I think it will help. Stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.22,0:42:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且彈劾可以被否決\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Impeachment can be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.86,0:42:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是我們要避免的\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But that's we need to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.42,0:42:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望彈劾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want impeachment...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.08,0:42:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要打一場明知會輸的仗\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Why fight a losing battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.07,0:42:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在眾議院是多數黨\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We have a majority in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.03,0:42:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.06,0:42:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果本黨不能和一個汙點總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}But if this party fails to distance itself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.77,0:42:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劃清界限\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}from a toxic president...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.88,0:42:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在做長遠打算\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We're thinking ahead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.64,0:42:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會找你就法案的事和解\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's why I came to you about the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.12,0:42:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不值得為它翻臉\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Because it wasn't worth burning a bridge over.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.31,0:42:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長遠來講  我們合作的好處更多\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}In the long run we have a lot more to gain by working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.86,0:42:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.90,0:42:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在《電訊報》採訪的時候說你會\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You said in the Telegraph article that you would sta--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.66,0:42:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必須那麼說\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.96,0:42:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的辦公室跟總統的只隔了三間屋子\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}My office is three doors down from the president's.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.34,0:42:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能公開詆譭他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't publicly deride him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.34,0:42:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我來做\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.83,0:42:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們希望你做你最拿手的  拉選票\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}We want you to do what you do so well: whip the votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.60,0:43:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能背叛總統\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I can't abandon the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.39,0:43:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果這個黨救了他\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}If the party rescues him,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.39,0:43:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將在中期選舉時失去50個席位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}we'll lose 50 seats in the House in the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.39,0:43:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會失去你在領導層的地位\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You will lose your position in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.07,0:43:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要花十年\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it will take us a decade
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.54,0:43:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重新贏得選民的信任\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}to regain the trust of the electorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.37,0:43:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只求你肯聽取意見\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}All we're asking is that you have an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.25,0:43:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾就是如此\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Claire kept an open mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.65,0:43:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得以修改性侵法案\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}and you'll pass sexual assault reform as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.08,0:43:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能把彈劾和...\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}You can't possibly compare impeachment to --
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.31,0:43:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是舉個例子  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's an illustration, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.22,0:43:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說明未來會怎麼樣\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Of what the future looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.11,0:43:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們提出的  是進步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What we offer is progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.83,0:43:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並保證日後還會有更多進步\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}With a promise of more to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.98,0:43:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這隻是個開始  傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's only the beginning, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.23,0:43:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,堅決  務實  記得嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Ruthless pragmatism, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.12,0:43:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才選你做黨鞭\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}That's why I wanted you to be the whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.96,0:43:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們三個是同一類人\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}The three of us, we're cut from the same cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.25,0:43:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統先生\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.37,0:44:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我做的  幾乎是叛國\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}what you're asking is just shy of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.13,0:44:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎  也就是政治\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Just shy. Which is politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.41,0:44:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心  那很易碎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Be careful. It's delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.32,0:44:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.30,0:44:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一件我做了很久的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Something I've been working on for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.04,0:44:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要完成了\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}And it's nearly finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.14,0:44:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傑姬\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.17,0:44:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幫我們完成吧\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Help us finish it.
